TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
Do you know anything about cults in the area?
Text: 이 근처 사교에 대해 아는 게 있나?

TextEng: You knows about cults, maybe?
What's going on in Luskan?
What go on in city?
Can I ask you some directions?
Me need directions.
Where is the nearest inn?
Where is the nearest temple?
Is there a place to buy equipment nearby?
Me look for place to sleep.
Me look for temple.
Me need place to buy stuff.
Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
No, me have other question.
Who are you?
Who be you?
I want to speak to you about Yvette's baby.
Me want talk 'bout Yvette's baby.
Text: 나 이베트 아기 얘기 하고 싶어.

TextEng: Be reasonable. Maybe we could work out some kind of deal.
Text: 좀 이성적으로 굴지. 어떻게 거래를 해볼까?

TextEng: How'd you like me to pry the child from your cold, dead hands?
Text: 차가운 네 시체 손에서 아이를 비틀어 빼내면 어떨까?

TextEng: Fine. Keep it. I want to ask you about something else anyway.
Text: 좋아. 가지고 있어. 어차피 다른 걸 물어볼 게 있어.

TextEng: We make deal, maybe?
You give baby or me just kill you and takes it from you.
Text: 아기 내놔. 아니면 널 죽이고 뺏는다.

TextEng: Fine. Me no want it. Me want ask 'bout something else.
Text: 좋아. 그건 안 원해. 다른 거 물어볼래.

TextEng: 1000 gp... deal.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I won't give you more than 250 gp.
That's it. Hand over the child... now.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That too much. Me give 250 gp.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그거 너무 많아. 나 금화 250개 줄게.

TextEng: That it! You hands over baby... now!
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Take the 250 gp. The next person who comes for the baby might not be so generous.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 금화 250이라도 챙기는게 좋을 걸. 다음에 아기를 찾으러 오는 녀석은 이렇게 후하지 않을 테니까.

TextEng: Fine. 400 gp... deal.
250 gp? Deal.
I'm done haggling. Time to kill you!
Me not argue no more. Now me kill you!!
Text: 더는 말싸움 안 해. 이제 너 죽인다!!

TextEng: I'm not going to 'buy' the child from you!
Me not 'buy' baby from you!
I can't afford to spend that much on this.
Text: 그 정도 돈을 쓸 형편이 안 된다.

TextEng: Me not afford that much for this.
I'm not buying the child for that much!
Text: 그 가격에 아이를 살 수는 없어!

TextEng: Me no spend so much for baby!
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Calm down. I don't mean you any harm.
Get out of my way! I'll take whatever I want!
I was just leaving.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You be calm. Me means no harm.
You get out of way! Me take what I wants!!
Text: 비켜! 나 원하는 건 다 가져가!!

TextEng: Me was just going.
I'm here to talk to you about Yvette's baby.
Me here to talks 'bout Yvette's baby.
Yvette doesn't intend to raise the child in the brothel.
Text: 이베트는 사창가에서 아이를 키울 생각이 없어.

TextEng: But she not wants to raise baby in brothel.
Text: 근데 그녀는 사창가에서 아기 키우기 싫어해.

TextEng: Let's not argue over this, sir. Hand over the child... now.
Text: 이 문제로 말다툼하지 말자고. 아이를 넘겨... 지금 당장.

TextEng: Me not going to argue. You gives me baby... now.
Text: 나 말싸움 안 해. 아기 줘... 지금.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I can take the child from you. I would rather you gave her to me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 내 힘으로 얼마든지 아이를 데려올 수 있어. 하지만 네가 스스로 넘겨주는 게 나을걸.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me can takes baby from you. Me prefer you gives her to me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나도 힘으로 아기 뺏을 수 있어. 근데 네가 주는 게 좋아.

TextEng: I would have to kill you, I suppose.
Me woulds kill you, me guesses.
Fine. Let's try to work out a deal, shall we?
Fine. We makes deal, okay?
All right, then. Now you die. <StartAction>[Attack]</Start>
Okays, then. You die now. <StartAction>[Attack]</Start>
*Sigh* Then you leave me little choice. <StartAction>[Attack]</Start>
*Sigh* You leaves me no choice. <StartAction>[Attack]</Start>
What wizards?
